'''乙酸鉈(III)'''是一種[[乙酸根|乙酸根]]和[[鉈|鉈]]的鹽類，化學式Tl(C<sub>2</sub>H<sub>3</sub>O<sub>2</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。在[[微生物學|微生物學]]中做為選擇性[[培养基|培养基]]<ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC378124/ Evaluation of Thallium Acetate-Citrate Medium for Isolation of Enterococci]</ref>，乙酸鉈有毒<ref name="Organization2008">{{cite book|author=World Health Organization|title=Anthrax in humans and animals|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=EKYihvnaA7oC&pg=PA139|accessdate=23 February 2011|year=2008|publisher=World Health Organization|isbn=978-92-4-154753-6|pages=139–|archive-date=2014-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140628163832/http://books.google.com/books?id=EKYihvnaA7oC&pg=PA139|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但也可做為脫髮劑，8mg/kg的劑量就會造成急性中毒，成人的最小致死劑量在12mg/kg<ref>{{cite web | url=http://119.78.242.243:8080/kexie/news.asp?id=144 | title=铊、玻璃和人——从两桩铊中毒事件说起 | publisher=中国科学院上海硅酸盐研究所 | accessdate=2015-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520034404/http://119.78.242.243:8080/kexie/news.asp?id=144 | archive-date=2015-05-20 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==制备==
80%的乙酸和[[三氧化二铊|三氧化二铊]]反应，产物在[[乙酸酐|乙酸酐]]中结晶，可以得到乙酸铊。<ref>Kolling, Orland W.; Mawdsley, Elizabeth A. Anhydrous thallium(III) acetate. ''Transactions of the Kansas Academy of Science'', 1971. 74 (1): 38-43. DOI:10.2307/3627666</ref>

